---
title: Middle Eastern Lamb & Veggie Mash Pie with Mixed Leaf Salad
description: We like to think this pie will baffle and delight your senses in equal measure. At first, the unexpected tahini crust on this Middle Eastern dish may throw you for a loop – but when you taste it, you may find it hard to go back to bland old pastry after this mashed veggie top surprise.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
